ingredients: ENRICHED FLOUR BLEACHED (WHEAT FLOUR, NIACIN, FERROUS SULFATE, THIAMIN MONONITRATE, RIBOFLAVIN, FOLIC ACID), WATER, SUGAR, SOYBEAN AND PALM OIL, BAKING POWDER (SODIUM ACID PYROPHOSPHATE, BAKING SODA, SODIUM ALUMINUM PHOSPHATE). CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF: DEXTROSE HYDROGENATED PALM OIL, VITAL WHEAT GLUTEN, SALT, POTASSIUM CHLORIDE, FRACTIONATED PALM OIL, MONO AND DIGLYCERIDES, XANTHAN GUM, PROPYLENE GLYCOL ALGINATE, PRESERVATIVES (TBHQ AND CITRIC ACID), BUTTER, BETA CAROTENE (FOR COLOR), NATURAL AND ARTIFICIAL FLAVOR.
